Proto-Proposal
---
Indenture

Amend Rule 1714 to read :

   An Overdue Payment Order that is a number of Blots is that
   number of Overdue Blots.  A Lawless Player is a Player who has more
   than 30 Overdue Blots.

   Whenever a Player is Lawless and is eir own Executor, the Justiciar,
   or the Speaker if the Lawless Player holds the Office of Justiciar,
   shall conduct an Open Auction to Indenture that Player, as defined in
   other Rules.

   At the end of the Auction, the Herald shall vacate all Blots of the
   Lawless Player and bill that Player for 5 Indulgences.

Enact a Rule, titled "Auction to Indenture", reading :

   Whenever the Rules call for an Auction to Indenture a Player, all
   Active Players, with the exception of the Player whose Indenture is
   being auctioned, shall be eligible. The Bank shall be the Seller.

   The Winner of the Auction shall become the Executor of the 
   Indentured Player for a period of one month.

---

